This reading is to document the process of launching the robot in the forest environment

Repository link: faiza-khatri/go2_ros2_sim_py

To get Gazebo running:
ros2 launch gazebo_sim launch_sim.launch.py

Set TROT mode:
ros2 topic pub --once /robot1/robot_mode quadropted_msgs/msg/RobotModeCommand "{mode: 'TROT', robot_id: 1}"
Teleop:
ros2 run teleop_twist_keyboard teleop_twist_keyboard --ros-args -r /cmd_vel:=/robot1/cmd_vel



